Before any new research, code the verbatims. Group by:

Onboarding stage they reference (signup / setup / first task / invite / activation)
Emotion expressed (confused / frustrated / abandoned / overwhelmed / disappointed)
Specific friction named (vs. vague dissatisfaction)
This usually surfaces 3-5 friction clusters, not 200 problems. You'll likely find one or two dominate.

